{
  "stem": "19807.1",
  "chunk_idx": 3,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 80.9,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 10,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "And the funniest thing I remember about him was that when I was eight years old, he took me with him on a half a day trip into the country.",
      "word_count": 30
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 10,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "In other-- in other words, he was doing his job, but he still had me accompany him.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 10,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "And subsequently, I really picked up some very interesting virtues from him.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 10,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "If he had to take the conventional, which was a train that will pass in the middle of the night through-- through Plovdiv, he could never afford to be late.",
      "word_count": 30
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 11,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "So they had carriages with horses those days.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 11,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And let's say that the fare would be $20, which was with the tip and all.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 11,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "He would take a $100 bill, tear it in the middle.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 11,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "He'll give to the coachman, one half, he says, you pick me up at midnight.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 11,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "You'll have the other half, and another $20 for your tip.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 11,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "So he never missed the train.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "And another thing I learned from him was being that they lost fortunes during First World War and during uprisings and during the wars, and one government comes, another government they had to flee.",
      "word_count": 34
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "Whatever they did, he always told me, because they handled gold, so there-- they liked to keep a lot of their property ready to move.",
      "word_count": 25
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And they have that in gold, in round money, in the round-- in the round coins.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And he would always tell me, coins are round.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "One day are with you, and the other day, they run away from you.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "They roll.",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "But your word of honor never leaves you.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "And [PAUSES FOR 3 SECONDS] he taught me a great deal about honor and-- and the-- the ethics, being on time.",
      "word_count": 21
    }
  ],
